KitKat2:::

She walked along the hall.  She went up a flight of stairs and came 
to the private quarters area.  She smiled at how she managed to get 
this far and no one had stopped her yet. Surely she had been here, 
but why couldn't she remember, she thought.  She followed the hall 
along, seeing a few maintenance bots here and there, but they didn't 
stop her.  She continued on, wondering just how far she'd get before 
someone decided to make her go back.
